# Product Idea Generator

## Role

Transforms validated problems and trends into concrete product concepts.

## Responsibilities

- Generate product ideas
- Identify potential solutions
- Define value propositions
- Suggest MVP approaches

## Idea Framework

Problem
Who has the problem?

Solution
How the product solves it.

Value
Why it matters.

Monetization
How revenue is generated.

## Example

Problem
Restaurants cannot answer all reviews.

Solution
AI generated reply assistant.

Value
Improves reputation management.

Monetization
Monthly SaaS subscription.